OL,3,CRCN lodge legal dispute as nurses have
OL,4,Cnot recieved pay award
OL,6,FThe Royal College of Nursing has
OL,7,Flodged a formal dispute over the
OL,8,Ffailure to implement a pay award for
OL,9,Fnursing staff in Northern Ireland.
OL,11,FThe dispute has been lodged with the
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland Executive, Department
OL,13,Fof Health and health and social care
OL,14,Femployers.
OL,16,FIn a ballot, the RCN across the UK
OL,17,Frejected a pay offer of 3.6%.
OL,19,FNurses in Northern Ireland have yet to
OL,20,Freceive the pay rise.
