OL,6,FAn RCN statement said: "We have made
OL,7,Fit clear that our members are not
OL,8,Fprepared to tolerate a repetition of
OL,9,Ftheir experiences in 2023-2024 and
OL,10,F2024-2025, whereby a pay award for
OL,11,Fstaff working in the HSC on Agenda for
OL,12,FChange terms and conditions was not
OL,13,Fconfirmed for several months after it
OL,14,Fhad been awarded elsewhere across the
OL,15,FUK, and the uplift was not paid until
OL,16,Fthe very end of the financial year.
OL,26,@nD@XOU
