OL,3,CRCN lodge legal dispute as nurses have
OL,4,Cnot recieved pay award
OL,6,F"Despite the recent welcome
OL,7,Fintervention of the Health Minister
OL,8,F(Mike Nesbitt) in issuing his
OL,9,Fministerial direction, it appears that
OL,10,Fwe are, once again, in the same
OL,11,Fposition."
OL,13,FRita Devlin, RCN Northern Ireland
OL,14,Fexecutive director said: "Nursing and
OL,15,Fother healthcare staff in Northern
OL,16,FIreland are once again on the brink of
OL,17,Fstepping out of pay parity with
OL,18,Fcolleagues across the UK.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@JO]vD@ZOU
