OL,3,CRCN lodge legal dispute as nurses have
OL,4,Cnot recieved pay award
OL,6,F"We have worked tirelessly to try and
OL,7,Fensure that this does not happen again
OL,8,Fbut there has been a failure in some
OL,9,Fpolitical quarters to listen.
OL,11,F"Our members do not understand why,
OL,12,Fyet again, they are being treated by
OL,13,Ftheir own Executive as second-class
OL,14,Fcitizens and why, every year, the need
OL,15,Fto formulate a modest pay offer
OL,16,Fappears to catch the Executive
OL,17,Funprepared.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
