OL,3,CRCN lodge legal dispute as nurses have
OL,4,Cnot recieved pay award
OL,6,F"The issue of pay should be accounted
OL,7,Ffor in every year's budget and a
OL,8,Ffailure to do this is a failure of
OL,9,Fgovernment."
OL,11,FMs Devlin added: "Without staff there
OL,12,Fis simply no health service, and we
OL,13,Fare at an absolute loss to explain
OL,14,Fthis attitude towards nursing staff
OL,15,Fwho are the largest professional group
OL,16,Fin the health service.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@LO]sD@ROU
