OL,3,CRCN lodge legal dispute as nurses have
OL,4,Cnot recieved pay award
OL,6,F"As our recent pay consultation has
OL,7,Fshown, nursing staff in Northern
OL,8,FIreland and across the UK, don't
OL,9,Fbelieve a 3.6% pay rise is enough, but
OL,10,Fto not even get that is an insult."
OL,12,FIn a statement issued through the
OL,13,FUlster Unionist Party, Nr Nesbitt said
OL,14,Fhe shared the frustration of the RCN.
OL,16,FHe added: "In May, I announced that I
OL,17,Fwas triggering the ministerial
OL,18,Fdirection process to achieve delivery
OL,19,Fof these pay increases as soon as
OL,20,Fpossible.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@cO]xD@KOU
