OL,6,F"That reflected my commitment to
OL,7,Fmaintaining pay parity with England.
OL,9,F"In line with the ministerial
OL,10,Fdirection process, my decision was
OL,11,Freferred to the wider Executive.
OL,13,F"Unfortunately, that's where it still
OL,14,Fsits.
OL,16,F"Our health workers deserve so much
OL,17,Fbetter."
